      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Moderate precipitation, locally heavy; snow at higher altitudes. The weather conditions will give rise to increasing and thorough wetting of the snowpack over a wide area. Snow cover and snow depth vary greatly depending on exposure and elevation. At low and intermediate altitudes a little snow is lying on south facing slopes. Weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on shady slopes."
